-- ALTER VIEW univmed.dim_forca_vendas
-- as
SELECT
[KEY_TERRITORIO_CICLO]
,[BU]
,[DIVISAO]
,[NOME_GD]
,[NOME_GR]
,[NOME_REPRESENTANTE]
,[MUDID]
,[TERRITORIO]
,[TERRITORIO_GD]
,[TERRITORIO_GR]
,[EMAIL_REP]
,[CICLO]
,[ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Universo Medico/dimensao_forca_vendas.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) with (
[KEY_TERRITORIO_CICLO]     VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[BU]					   VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIVISAO]				   VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_GD]				   VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_GR]				   VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_REPRESENTANTE]	   VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MUDID]				   VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO]			   VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_GD]		   VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_GR]		   VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[EMAIL_REP]			   VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CICLO]				   VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]	   VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) as ROW
